  "body": "### Description\n\n*Type*: Feature\n\n*Summary*: Users should be able to add/remove emoji reactions to messages. All chats and messages should be supported including own messages, send/receive commands and replies. SNT kudos are not in scope of this issue.\n\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7532782/49282915-9eb61080-f490-11e8-95b5-99ed7a527302.png\" width=\"200\">\n\nInteractive designs: https://framer.cloud/ObAKy\n\n#### Acceptance Criteria\n\nTBD\n\n### Additional Information\n* Operating System: all platforms\n\n\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://framer.cloud/ObAKy/3/framer/social-1200x630.png\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div><strong><a href=\"https://framer.cloud/ObAKy\">Threads and Reactions</a></strong></div><div>Press and hold on messages to get reactions, click to open threads. üëØ‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è \nfeedback: maciej.stateofus.eth </div></blockquote>",
